iented merchant service providers offer web design assistance.","<strong>Shopping Cart </strong><br/>Even with a sleek website, a good shopping cart gives visitors to your site a convenient checkout method. All of the payment processing occurs in the background. Be sure that any gateway you select is compatible with the shopping cart you plan to implement. Generally speaking, most gateways are compatible with hundreds of shopping carts. For the typical web entrepreneur, a shopping cart is the best way to accept credit cards online. If you have particularly broad programming resources available, it is entirely possible to customize your entire checkout and payment process.","<strong>Security Certificate </strong><br/>There are a huge number of companies online that can get you set up with a merchant account. Make sure that the gateway they use is PCI DSS (Payment Card Industry Data Security Standard) compliant. In order to legally process credit cards online, it s critical to get a security certificate. Firms such as VeriSign or McAfee can certify your site if your payment process meets their requirements. As long as the credit card verification process you institute on your site includes AVS, CVV2 and address verification along with SSL data transmission, certification should be a breeze. <br/><br/>"]},"id":"aee33993-a4dc-491a-990f-b739deffa8d6","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"article_page_4700","url":"/what-you-need-to-know-about-payment-gateways-before-you-get-started","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"david-aamodt","url":"/author/david-aamodt","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"David Aamodt","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"KSrbtPL3kuxXqpPPF63Dwn","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2010-07-29T19:37:12Z","datePublished":"2010-07-29T19:37:12Z","name":"What You Need to Know about Payment Gateways Before You Get Started","synopsis":"A payment gateway isn’t a comprehensive sol